data.description: This 2-story home is on a 1.5 acres lot in the City of chilton and offers 4BR/1BA/2287 sqft. Simulated wood floor throughout. The property has a garden area behind the 2-car garage, a shed and many shade offering mature trees. It is close to shopping, dining, schools, movies and many other activities.
